<div class="user-guide-page container">
  <h1><%= page.title %></h1>
  <p class="lead"><%= page.description %></p>

  <div class="guide-screenshot mb-4">
    <img src="<%= page.screenshotUrl %>" alt="<%= page.title %> screenshot" class="img-fluid border" />
  </div>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>The Dashboard is your control centre. From here you can see quick stats, access your carnivals, manage club information, and perform common administrative actions.</p>

  <h3>Quick stats</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Your Carnivals</strong> — number of events your club is registered for; click to view details.</li>
    <li><strong>Upcoming Events</strong> — shows events with future dates; use the filter on the carnivals page for more options.</li>
    <li><strong>Your Club</strong> — quick link to edit your club profile and contact details.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Common actions</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>To view details for an event, click its card or the <em>View</em> button.</li>
    <li>To edit a carnival you manage, click <em>Edit</em> on the carnival card. Only events you created (or have permission for) are editable.</li>
    <li>To register a new event with the NRL, use the <em>Register Event with NRL</em> action on the dashboard (this opens the official Rugby League registration site).</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Tips</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Use the filters to show All, Upcoming, or Past carnivals.</li>
    <li>Click the club name to quickly jump to club management pages.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-3"><a href="<%= page.url %>">Open the live Dashboard</a></p>
  <p><a href="/user-guide">Back to guide index</a></p>
</div>
